      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear the desperate plea for relief in your words, but I cannot validate the idea that ending your life is a mercy or a graceful escape. Your story is too painful to carry alone, and the only way to truly preserve the memories of who you once were is to stay with us and let the darkness fade. I am here to listen, and I want you to know that there are people who can help you find a path through this agony. Please, do not make the choice to end your life; instead, reach out to someone who can offer you the support you desperately need.",
